-[laughter]

33
00:01:45.189 --> 00:01:47.608
But you all played a huge part in that.

34
00:01:48.192 --> 00:01:51.111
Tiffany. you helped me
find my signature scent.

35
00:01:51.195 --> 00:01:53.739
-[laughs]
-Mrs. Campbell.

36
00:01:53.823 --> 00:01:55.866
you showed me the importance of an SPF.

37
00:01:57.451 --> 00:01:58.577
And Madison.

38
00:01:58.661 --> 00:02:01.497
my best friend of 12.5 years.

39
00:02:01.580 --> 00:02:04.375
I can't even count the number of times
you saved me

40
00:02:04.458 --> 00:02:05.960
from overplucking my eyebrows.

41
00:02:06.043 --> 00:02:07.920
-I know.
-If it weren't for you.

42
00:02:08.003 --> 00:02:10.923
