never to speak of that again.

66
00:03:04.935 --> 00:03:06.562
-[both laugh]
-Okay.

67
00:03:06.645 --> 00:03:08.188
Let's talk junior year.

68
00:03:08.272 --> 00:03:09.815
I'm assuming that you've put together

69
00:03:09.899 --> 00:03:11.692
