70
00:03:11.775 --> 00:03:14.528
-to dominate 11th grade.
-Uh. no.

71
00:03:15.821 --> 00:03:17.406
-It's a three-point plan.
-[gasps]

72
00:03:17.489 --> 00:03:18.824
-More concise. that's better.
-Mm-hmm.

73
00:03:18.908 --> 00:03:20.451
-Step one...
-Mm-hmm?

74
00:03:20.534 --> 00:03:22.453
...solidify our friendships
with the coolest senior girls

75
00:03:22.536 --> 00:03:24.955
so our reputations are firmly in place
when they graduate.

76
00:03:25.039 --> 00:03:26.165
-Obviously.
-Mm-hmm.

77
00:03:26.248 --> 00:03:27.583
-Mm-hmm.
-Step two.

78
00:03:27.666 --> 00:03:29.627
