79
00:03:29.710 --> 00:03:31.211
-Mm. that's inevitable.
-[laughs]

80
00:03:31.295 --> 00:03:34.548
And step three. and this is probably
the most important step of all...

81
00:03:34.632 --> 00:03:36.383
Mm-hmm.

82
00:03:36.467 --> 00:03:39.470
...have the most perfect first kiss
with the most perfect guy.

83
00:03:39.553 --> 00:03:41.096
[squeals] Let me guess.

84
00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:42.765
-Hot Josh?
-[stammers]

85
00:03:44.266 --> 00:03:45.601
Do you want me to talk to him for you?

86
00:03:45.684 --> 00:03:48.270
-No. I have a better idea.
-Okay.

87
00:03:48.354 --> 00:03:50.397
I'm gonna start a rumor
that he has a crush on me.

88
00:03:51.398 --> 00:03:53.734
And then he'll hear the rumor.
and he'll start to wonder... [gasps]

89
00:03:53.817 --> 00:03:54.944
"Do I have a crush on her?"

90
00:03:55.027 --> 00:03:57.571
And then we'll be
in the most perfect location together.

91
00:03:57.655 --> 00:04:00.199
A Bryan Adams song will start to play.

92
00:04:00.282 --> 00:04:01.700
and then he'll kiss me.

93
00:04:02.785 --> 00:04:05.204
-Or you could just talk to him now.
-[chuckles]

94
00:04:05.287 --> 00:04:07.414
-That's not really part of the plan--
-Oh. Josh!

95
00:04:07.498 --> 00:04:09.083
-Come here! Come here. come here.
-[Elle] M-Madison. Madison.

96
00:04:09.166 --> 00:04:12.378
-Plan. The plan.
-I will get right on that.

97
00:04:12.461 --> 00:04:14.463
-Yes. Mm.
-[Elle panting]

98
00:04:14.546 --> 00:04:15.965
Oh.

99
00:04:16.048 --> 00:04:17.257
Happy birthday.

100
00:04:17.341 --> 00:04:19.093
Thanks. Hot...

101
00:04:19.176 --> 00:04:22.096
Josh. You are so sweet.

102
00:04:22.179 --> 00:04:24.807
Uh. well. I'm-I'm really glad
Madison called me over.

103
00:04:24.890 --> 00:04:27.101
There's something I've been meaning
to talk to you about.

104
00:04:27.184 --> 00:04:28.811
Really?

105
00:04:28.894 --> 00:04:30.896
[♪ Bryan Adams sings
"Have You Ever Really Loved a Woman?"]

106
00:04:30.980 --> 00:04:32.731
♪ To really ♪

107
00:04:32.815 --> 00:04:34.274
♪ love a woman ♪

108
00:04:35.359 --> 00:04:37.820
-♪ To understand...
-So. I've been thinking about you.

109
00:04:37.903 --> 00:04:39.780
-actually.
-Yeah?

110
00:04:40.280 --> 00:04:41.782
And...

111
00:04:42.950 --> 00:04:44.702
[crowd] ♪ Happy birthday ♪

112
00:04:44.785 --> 00:04:46.912
♪ to you ♪

113
00:04:46.996 --> 00:04:48.038
