298
00:13:06.995 --> 00:13:08.371
-[Elle] Bruiser.
-[Bruiser whimpers]

299
00:13:08.455 --> 00:13:10.248
We have to give Seattle a shot.

300
00:13:10.332 --> 00:13:13.585
